      <title>在 zed 中配置 Augment Context Engine MCP </title>
      <link>https://jasminides.com/posts/%E5%9C%A8-zed-%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE-augment-context-engine-mcp/</link>
